{"type":"message","id":"1e202c36","parentId":"02a2ff82","timestamp":"2026-03-30T12:03:03.744Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"web_search:11","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"西安 耳鸣 医院推荐 西京医院 交大一附院 耳鼻喉科 真实评价\",\n  \"provider\": \"tavily\",\n  \"count\": 5,\n  \"tookMs\": 1576,\n  \"externalContent\": {\n    \"untrusted\": true,\n    \"source\": \"web_search\",\n    \"provider\": \"tavily\",\n    \"wrapped\": true\n  },\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"4fcdf5081cbd9087\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n西安哪个医院看耳鸣比较权威-医疗科普-百度健康\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"4fcdf5081cbd9087\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://m.baidu.com/bh/m/detail/ar_4892744381240138489?frsrcid=rec\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"6f18881679f2e4db\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n1. 交大二附院：综合性医院，耳鼻喉科经验丰富，设备先进。 · 2. 交大一附院：神经内科和耳鼻喉科实力强，耳鸣诊疗经验丰富。 · 3. 西京医院：全国前列综合医院，\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"6f18881679f2e4db\\\">>>\",\n      \"score\": 0.8539252\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"45192e5449c74124\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n西安哪些医院的耳鼻喉科比较权威？ - 知乎\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"45192e5449c74124\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.zhihu.com/question/578212138?write\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"118fb0a4300b6623\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n但是西安耳鼻喉的专科医院较少，所以西安好的耳鼻喉医院其实还是公里医院的耳鼻喉科室。最好的目前是西京医院，交大一附院，交大二附院，西安第四医院。\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"118fb0a4300b6623\\\">>>\",\n      \"score\": 0.8020137\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"fb31e9c49ff75543\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n陕西西安- 耳鸣推荐医院 - 好大夫在线\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"fb31e9c49ff75543\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.haodf.com/citiao/jibing-erming/tuijian-hospital-6101.html\",\n      \"snippet\": \"